5. Implement constraints to ensure that the cars do not collide, such as maintaining a minimum gap between cars and adjusting the velocity and acceleration of each car to avoid collisions. 

```matlab
function acc_des = IDM(v, v_lead, d, v0, T, a_max, a_min, b, s0)
   % calculates desired acceleration using IDM equation

   delta_v = v - v_lead;
   s_star = s0 + max(0, (v * T + (v * delta_v) / (2 * sqrt(a_max * b))));
   acc_des = a_max * (1 - (v/v0)^4 - (s_star/d)^2);
   if (d < 0)
      acc_des = min(acc_des, (v^2 * a_max) / (2 * abs(d)));
   end
end
```

